Title: Deems a person who engages in sexual conduct during the period of their probation with his or her supervising probation officer as being incapable of consent
Summary: Deems a person who engages in sexual conduct during the period of their probation with his or her supervising probation officer as being incapable of consent.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the penal law, in relation to deeming a person who engages in sexual conduct during the period of their probation with his or her supervising probation officer as being incapable of consent
